{"tid":1472820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本發布香港旅遊警示 1997移交後首例","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:57:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e65fe0e949ca42a25f87dec6080a1e244b820889","tid":1472820,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:23:02.000Z","msg":"日本外務省今（14）發布香港旅遊警示，15日生效；外務省指出衝突情勢可能升級，建議注意安全，屬於4級別中的最低1級警示。日本媒體報導，這是自1997年香港主權移交中國以來的首次警示。<br />\n<br />\n日本外務省今（14）發布香港旅遊警示，已於日本時間15日生效。外務省在說明中指出，因「逃犯條例」修例引發的相關抗議活動，動員情勢可能變化，例如出現游擊式抗議、或可見趨於升級的衝突。且抗議活動範圍也擴大到機場與部分觀光景點，估計混亂情勢可能持續，使香港的風險等級提高。<br />\n<br />\n日本外相河野太郎也在推特上轉發此警示，向日本國民發出提醒訊息。<br />\n<br />\n日本外務省的「旅遊警示」分為4級，數字越大，風險程度越高；1級是建議注意安全，2級是建議非必要勿前往，3級是建議暫勿前往，4級是建議撤離。<br />\n<br />\n日本駐港總領館7月底曾向在港日本國民發出通告，提醒避免前往潛在危險地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2884871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2884871&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=9b8610ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2884871&h=5828fe8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2884871</a>"},{"pid":"4578afe677225f1f53300063b7c702e7ff07dc5c","tid":1472820,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>求推求推! 香港人可以試下noise making protest! </strong><br />\n<br />\n[推膠招]全民係屋企都可以示威:Noise-Making抗爭法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a>"},{"pid":"4272d2575adb4c21cbdc09ab20071f49b925e17b","tid":1472820,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"發警示既國家都係好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a191bc47b3b2c89dfa0f9bd76f8c55ba7ea824d9","tid":1472820,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"3級啦 仲一級"},{"pid":"e74dd42ecda35b2b3245ff5a7da66049dbe97aa1","tid":1472820,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得太多post太亂？我地整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1472357/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1472357/page/1</a><br />\n包括行動方向、文宣方向、檢討、戰術等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===================================<br />\n大家可以幫手推呢個<br />\n又或者進一步將整合左既post既內容整合一次<br />\n將重點re-post上連登"},{"pid":"2fff6c515675827d377720606336e9ab60fdd89c","tid":1472820,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602207b915297e4307929977640c08eb6e6e59b2","tid":1472820,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"4級半啦"},{"pid":"86743341a30fcbe9c32f3faddd60af796ead5532","tid":1472820,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:52:20.000Z","msg":"不處理 不回應 不解決 <br />\n不認錯 不出現 不下台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fbd026d2b7d71e6e330ae113709153f77647d4","tid":1472820,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}